item.title: [PI] org. folder errors
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

There isn’t going to be an org folder. You should have a “deps” or sometimes a “libs” folder. That should contain all your .jars.
You need .jar for voting (looks like the gtlvote system) and that can be found on the gtlvote thread over on R-S.
You also needs the commons io jar, which can be found here.
